OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FMinisters face pressure to act on the
OL,7,Fcost of living as the Iran conflict
OL,8,Fthreatens to push prices higher.
OL,10,FOil prices have soared since the US
OL,11,Fand Israel began strikes on Iran,
OL,12,Fexceeding 100 dollars per barrel on
OL,13,FMonday.
OL,15,FAlthough prices fell back below 90
OL,16,Fdollars as US President Donald Trump
OL,17,Fsuggested the conflict was nearing a
OL,18,Fconclusion ` contradicting his own
OL,19,FDefence Department ` economists warned
OL,20,Fthat the war would mean inflation
OL,21,Fremains higher for longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FThe British Chambers of Commerce
OL,7,Fforecast that inflation would remain
OL,8,F"firmly above" the Bank of England's
OL,9,F2% target, noting the "highly
OL,10,Funcertain" global situation.
OL,12,FBoth Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fand Rachel Reeves have acknowledged
OL,14,Fthat the war is likely to cause
OL,15,Feconomic damage in the UK, with the
OL,16,FChancellor telling MPs it was "likely
OL,17,Fto put upward pressure on inflation"
OL,18,Fover the coming months.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]qD@WOUrD@JO]xD@_OUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
