OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FFollowing a call with her G7
OL,7,Fcounterparts on Monday, Ms Reeves said
OL,8,Fshe was ready to support "a co-
OL,9,Fordinated release" of international
OL,10,Foil reserves to ease the economic
OL,11,Fshock of the crisis.
OL,13,FShe also called for action to
OL,14,F"guarantee the security of vessels
OL,15,Fpassing through the Strait of Hormuz".
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@RO]vD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
