OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FMr Trump later took to social media to
OL,7,Fwarn that if Iran did "anything that
OL,8,Fstops the flow of Oil within the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz", that the United
OL,10,FStates would "make it virtually
OL,11,Fimpossible for Iran to ever be built
OL,12,Fback".
OL,14,FIn a post on Truth Social he wrote:
OL,15,F"If Iran does anything that stops the
OL,16,Fflow of Oil within the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz, they will be hit by the United
OL,18,FStates of America TWENTY TIMES HARDER
OL,19,Fthan they have been hit thus far.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@QO]rD@NOUtD@EO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,F"Additionally, we will take out easily
OL,7,Fdestroyable targets that will make it
OL,8,Fvirtually impossible for Iran to ever
OL,9,Fbe built back, as a Nation, again `
OL,10,FDeath, Fire, and Fury will reign upon
OL,11,Fthem ` But I hope, and pray, that it
OL,12,Fdoes not happen!
OL,14,F"This is a gift from the United States
OL,15,Fof America to China, and all of those
OL,16,FNations that heavily use the Hormuz
OL,17,FStrait. Hopefully, it is a gesture
OL,18,Fthat will be greatly appreciated."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
