OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FDespite asking the competition
OL,7,Fwatchdog to prevent wartime
OL,8,Fprofiteering, the Chancellor resisted
OL,9,Fcalls to cancel a planned increase in
OL,10,Ffuel duty in response to the oil price
OL,11,Fspike.
OL,13,FFuel duty has been frozen since 2011,
OL,14,Fand was cut by 5p in 2022 in response
OL,15,Fto Russia's full-scale invasion of
OL,16,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FAt her budget last year, Ms Reeves
OL,7,Fsaid the 5p cut would be unwound
OL,8,Fbetween September 2026 and March 2027,
OL,9,Fbut the Conservatives and Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats have called for her to
OL,11,Fchange course.
OL,13,FShadow chancellor Sir Mel Stride said:
OL,14,F"The latest developments in the Middle
OL,15,FEast make it even more important for
OL,16,FRachel Reeves to reverse course and
OL,17,Fscrap the rise in fuel duty she
OL,18,Fannounced at the budget."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
