OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey
OL,7,Fconfirmed the ship, currently docked
OL,8,Fat Portsmouth, would set sail "in the
OL,9,Fnext couple of days" before linking up
OL,10,Fwith US air defence vessels in the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FThe move is intended to bolster
OL,14,Fdefences against missiles and drones,
OL,15,Fparticularly around the British bases
OL,16,Fat Akrotiri and Dhekelia in Cyprus.
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
