CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FBut the Government has been accused of
OL,7,Fbeing slow to act, criticised for both
OL,8,Ffailing to deploy HMS Dragon in
OL,9,Fadvance of the US-Israeli strikes on
OL,10,FIran and the length of time it has
OL,11,Ftaken for the vessel to even leave
OL,12,Fport.
OL,14,FIt remains unclear how long the
OL,15,Fconflict will continue, with further
OL,16,Fstrikes reported in Tehran as Mr Trump
OL,17,Fclaimed the US operation was "very
OL,18,Fcomplete" and the Pentagon said
OL,19,FAmerica had "only just begun to fight".
OL,26,@yD@^OUzD@IO]{D@MOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
