OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773108185
OL,3,CUK faces inflation pressure as Iran
OL,4,Cconflict continues
OL,6,FThe US has also withdrawn non-
OL,7,Fessential diplomatic staff from Saudi
OL,8,FArabia amid continued Iranian
OL,9,Fretaliation, while the UK has
OL,10,Fwithdrawn the dependants of embassy
OL,11,Fstaff in the UAE "as a precautionary
OL,12,Fmeasure".
OL,14,FIsrael and Lebanon-based, Iran-backed
OL,15,Fmilitant group Hezbollah have also
OL,16,Fcontinued to exchange missile fire.
OL,26,@sD@ROUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
